Program: Outlook
Title: Replicating London's Speaker's Corner in Singapore
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrdj
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Free speech in Speaker's Corner in Hyde Park, London - soon to come to Singapore. Also, Joyce Jenje-Makwenda, Zimbabwe township music and how Louis Armstrong loved 'Skokiaan'. Finally, ancient Egypt and how to teach yourself hieroglyphs. Presented by Fred Dove.